description:
This is a free event being organised by GDG London and several other UK GDGs. Please RSVP on this Meetup to indicate to us your interest in the topic and the main event RSVP is at https://gdg.community.dev/events/details/google-gdg-london-presents-flutter-engage-extended-uk-ireland/

Hope to see you there! :)
title: Flutter Engage Extended UK & Ireland
